{"tid":2398854,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係突然玩氣槍，之後拎到世界賽前幾名?","createTime":"2021-02-07T15:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T18:10:34.000Z","uid":370862,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa65677640c83ed61aaae7f16c42ccc34c13f54","tid":2398854,"uid":370862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"有時都會諗，通常運動都係要講求練習，而且體能體力都幾重要<br />\n就算你有異常既肌肉 / 敏捷，你都係要練先會有好既成績<br />\n但射擊，尤其係用槍，好似真係唔多理會體力、練習?<br />\n正如有d人真係可以一玩射擊已經可以好準<br />\n當然，唔係話射擊完全唔洗練，但係相對上好似練習唔算要太辛苦，而且都冇咩年齡限制<br />\n<br />\n咁到底有冇人真係係無啦啦玩氣槍發現原來自己幾勁<br />\n之後真係去玩下，結果拎埋世界賽前幾名?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bc939913ceab79e21fbb01d22f506b565d25dd","tid":2398854,"uid":224510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"奧運果類氣槍打靶要求都幾高<br />\n唔係射一兩槍就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e845af7813fd14d4f884b81fbc334aa3ca4782","tid":2398854,"uid":381265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"主角光環"},{"pid":"ccda26452d8dd7c9024452ec792d0f6030bee789","tid":2398854,"uid":59910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"ipsc 一定唔係"},{"pid":"6db05364a5e9996c3fad7623e0a8fe67117956a9","tid":2398854,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"玩街機d槍驚算唔算<br />\n利申 一下就爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c63e543b65796423d7d66c3c2339eac72bd570","tid":2398854,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6db05364a5e9996c3fad7623e0a8fe67117956a9","tid":2398854,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"玩街機d槍驚算唔算<br />\n利申 一下就爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"咁撚廢一下就俾人爆頭<img src=\"/assets/fac